# Ejemplos de Peticiones HTTP para SubTracker API

## Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Obtener todas las suscripciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions

###

### Crear suscripción - Netflix (USD Mensual)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Netflix",
  "price": 15.99,
  "currency": "USD",
  "frequency": "MONTHLY",
  "paymentDate": 15
}

